It's automatically distributes the traffic into mutiple targets such as
    EC2 Instances
    Container
    IP address - (ENI - Network Interface)
    Lambda functions

It can handle the varying load of your application traffic in Single or across mutiple AZ. not region.

Three types of Load balancer:
    Application LB
    Network LB
    Classic LB

It provides the high availability, Automatic scaling & Robust security.